Full licence text:  ./LICENSE-CODE.txt
Online:             https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Apache-2.0 was chosen (rather than MIT) specifically because
several of the CODE components use AI / LLM integrations and an
explicit patent-licence grant protects downstream users against
submarine-patent claims.

