6. DATA QUALITY DISCLAIMER
================================================================

The cost data is compiled from public, licensed, and originally
collected sources and normalised for cross-language and
cross-regional comparability. It is NOT a substitute for formal
bids, quotations, or country-specific professional cost
publications (RSMeans, BCIS, Batiprix, Baukosteninformations-
zentrum, RICS NRM, etc.). Licensor makes no representation that
prices are current, complete, or accurate for any specific
project. Use at Your own risk - see Sections 5 and 6 of the
CC BY 4.0 legal code for the full warranty disclaimer.

